text: Tya or TYA may refer to: ==Languages== * Tauya language, a language in Papua New Guinea ==Places== * Tya, Sogn og Fjordane, a river in Sogn og Fjordane county, Norway * Tya, Trøndelag, a river in Trøndelag county, Norway ==Other== * Tya (unit), a measure of time meaning "thousands of years ago" * Theatre for Young Audiences (TYA), a branch of theatre arts attended by or created for younger audiences.
title: Tya
